{
  "texts": [
    "From software design, development, testing, release to business operation, all links of the team work together to shorten the development life cycle of the entire application.",
    "Dev0ps implements the concept of \"shift left,\" shifting the responsibility for delivering high-quality products to all members of the development and operations teams.",
    "As a result, productivity is improved, and programs can be iterated quickly to meet changing business requirements.As for why security is critical in DevOps, this is mainly because DevOps focuses on fast delivery, but this can lead to the introduction of security vulnerabilities.",
    "Inadequate security can lead to problems such as data breaches, malicious intrusions, and reputational damage.",
    "By integrating security measures into the DevOps process, you can ensure continuous monitoring and feedback to quickly detect and respond to potential security threats."
  ]
}